The CI/CD pipeline is set up to automate testing and deployment processes. Ensure that all changes are tested and validated before merging into the main branch.

## Getting Started

1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/yourusername/smart-health-monitoring.git
   cd smart-health-monitoring
   ```

2. Install dependencies:
   ```bash
   pip install -r requirements.txt
   ```

3. Start the services:
   ```bash
   docker-compose up
   ```

4. Access the API at `http://localhost:8000`.

